AutomaticTransactionRemoval is a BusinessTask
    owned by ar

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                AutomaticTransactionRemovalReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is a ReceivableCompany 
        TranReasonCode          is an ApplicationAdjustmentReason
        OprCode                 is Alpha size 10
        PayReasonCode           is an ApplicationAdjustmentReason
        SortOption              is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Customer value is "C"
                Dpd      value is "D"
                    default label is "DPD"
                Amount   value is "A"
        RemovePostDate          is Date
        UpdateOption            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        FrCustomer              is a Customer 
        ToCustomer              is a Customer 
        FrBalance               is Decimal size 17.2
        ToBalance               is Decimal size 17.2
        FrRiskCode              is AlphaUpper size 1
        ToRiskCode              is AlphaUpper size 1
        FrMajClass              is a CustomerMajorClass
        ToMajClass              is a CustomerMajorClass
        FrMinClass              is a CustomerMinorClass
        	context of FrMajClass
        ToMinClass              is a CustomerMinorClass
        	context of ToMajClass
        FrAnlyst                is a CreditAnalyst
        ToAnlyst                is a CreditAnalyst
        FrCustSalesman          is a SalesRepresentative
        ToCustSalesman          is a SalesRepresentative
        FrCustTermsCd           is a TermsCode
        ToCustTermsCd           is a TermsCode

        FrDpd                   is Numeric size 4
        ToDpd                   is Numeric size 4
        FrDueDate               is Date
        ToDueDate               is Date
        FrAmount                is Decimal size 17.2
        ToAmount                is Decimal size 17.2
        TranType1               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                All        value is "A"
                CreditMemo value is "C"
                DebitMemo  value is "D"
                Invoice    value is "I"
                Payment    value is "P"
        TranType2               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                CreditMemo value is "C"
                DebitMemo  value is "D"
                Invoice    value is "I"
                Payment    value is "P"
        TranType3               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                CreditMemo value is "C"
                DebitMemo  value is "D"
                Invoice    value is "I"
                Payment    value is "P"
        TranType4               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                CreditMemo value is "C"
                DebitMemo  value is "D"
                Invoice    value is "I"
                Payment    value is "P"
        DebitType1              is AlphaUpper size 2
            States
                Chargeback    value is "CB"
                FinanceCharge value is "FC"
                Grouping      value is "GP"
                ReturnToMaker value is "RM"
                    default label is "Return to Maker"
        DebitType2              is AlphaUpper size 2
            States
                Chargeback    value is "CB"
                FinanceCharge value is "FC"
                Grouping      value is "GP"
                ReturnToMaker value is "RM"
                    default label is "Return to Maker"
        DebitType3              is AlphaUpper size 2
            States
                Chargeback    value is "CB"
                FinanceCharge value is "FC"
                Grouping      value is "GP"
                ReturnToMaker value is "RM"
                    default label is "Return to Maker"
        DebitType4              is AlphaUpper size 2
            States
                Chargeback    value is "CB"
                FinanceCharge value is "FC"
                Grouping      value is "GP"
                ReturnToMaker value is "RM"
                    default label is "Return to Maker"
        ExemptDisputes          is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        FrCurrency              is a Currency
        ToCurrency              is a Currency
        FrProcessLevel          is a ReceivableProcessLevel
        ToProcessLevel          is a ReceivableProcessLevel
        FrTranTermsCd           is a TermsCode
        ToTranTermsCd           is a TermsCode
        FrTranSalesman          is a SalesRepresentative
        ToTranSalesman          is a SalesRepresentative
        FrActivity              is a Project
        ToActivity              is a Project

    Parameter Rules
        Company
            required
        SortOption
        	initial value is "C"
            default to "C"
        UpdateOption
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        TranType1
        	initial value is "A"
            default to "A"
        ExemptDisputes
        	initial value is "Y"
            default to "Y"
        PayReasonCode
			required  
        	constraint (PayReasonCode != "CURR")
				"CURRIsAReservedReasonCode"
		TranReasonCode
			constraint (PayReasonCode != "CURR")
				"CURRIsAReservedReasonCode"
			required  

    Actions
        AutomaticTransactionRemoval is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
